{"tid":583850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警否認非法性交 今獲准候審期間離港外遊10天","createTime":"2018-03-07T10:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T16:41:26.000Z","uid":47359,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe42334621b26c32f2b78c3a5d42d60c64338a0","tid":583850,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:45:09.000Z","msg":"休班警否認非法性交 今獲准候審期間離港外遊10天<br />\n即時要聞  2018-02-15 11:13:39 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/184506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F184506_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=cecd0773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被告陳健敏(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n警員涉嫌於2013年1月至10月期間，於屯門區與一名當時15歲的女童性交，早前被控與年齡在16歲以下的女童非法性交罪，他今在屯門裁判法院否認控罪，裁判官將案排期至4月17日審理。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露將有5名控方證人出庭，並申請事主可於屏風後作供及使用特別通道進出法庭，裁判官批准申請。<br />\n<br />\n被告陳健敏（38歲）可繼續保釋並不得干擾控方證人。辯方則指因已報旅行團外遊，申請候審期間有10天離港，在控方不反對下，裁判官批准申請但將保釋金由2,000元提高至5,000元。"},{"pid":"411f66ec26115a646aee6c14f8ab08a4218bb51f","tid":583850,"uid":103156,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"已報炮兵團"},{"pid":"7815aa9c3323dc779fd5b476266071cdbdcd52f8","tid":583850,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88054629bf3c35d11a9b6e65ffb1f9f460a759aa","tid":583850,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:22:38.000Z","msg":"仲唔有得屌好屌呀～<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n返嚟入册冇得屌架啦"},{"pid":"93b7c214f4355268bf11b102d65a807896928d68","tid":583850,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T13:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101a100f150cf69bbc9640c9fba1288515d6f780"